body.name: Lego Icons Succulents 10309 Artificial Plants Set for Adults, Home Decor, Birthday, Creative Housewarming Gifts, Botanical Collection, Flower Bouquet Kit
features: Home Décor - Features 9 different LEGO artificial decorative plants creating a succulents low-maintenance display to enhance your office or home décor
Realistic Bloom - Bring nature indoors with this LEGO set for adults! Inspired by real-life plants and flowers, this set adds a contemporary touch to your space
Vibrant Design - Admire the different shapes, textures and colours that make up the display, with each plant mirroring a real-life variety
Personalized Plants - Customise your display by presenting the plants together, in small groups or individually to create a personalized look. Get creative and let your personality shine through!

Endless Possibilities - Combine alongside many of the unique adult building sets from the LEGO Botanical Collection, including Flower Bouquet (10280), Wildflower Bouquet (10313), Dried Flower Centerpiece (10314), and Orchid (10311)
Perfect Gift - Great for any occasion, whether as a gift for Valentine's Day, Mother's Day, birthday, anniversary, or just because
Dimensions - This buildable model measures over 5 in. (13 cm) high, 6.5 in. (17 cm) wide and 6.5 in. (17 cm) deep. Contains 771 pieces
body.description: Succulents are a popular way to introduce plants into the office or to enhance your home décor. Now you can enjoy a mindful building project as you create an elegant plant display for your living space with this LEGO Succulents (10309) building kit for adults. Take your time crafting all the details of the 9 different succulents – each inspired by a real-life variety. Then show off your creativity with the ultimate low-maintenance plant display. Each succulent comes in its own small container. Combine them to create 1 arrangement, display in small groups or show them off individually throughout your home, office or dorm room. This set also makes a great gift idea for plant lovers, and with 3 separate instruction booklets it’s the perfect project to enjoy with friends and family. These make great birthday decorations and unique housewarming gifts. Discover the space to be mindful and the time to relax with buildable models designed specifically for adults from the LEGO Botanical Collection.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Refreshing and Creative Touch to Home Decor - LEGO Icons Succulents Set!
reviews.reviewText: I recently indulged in the LEGO Icons Succulents 10309 Set, and it has been a delightful and refreshing addition to my home decor. As an adult fan of LEGO and a lover of plants, this set perfectly bridges my interests, offering a unique and creative experience.The first thing that stands out about this set is the intricate detail and realistic design of the succulents. Each plant is distinct and beautifully crafted, showcasing a variety of shapes, sizes, and colors that truly mimic real-life succulents. The attention to detail is impressive, making each piece a small work of art.Building the set was a therapeutic and enjoyable process. The instructions are clear and easy to follow, making the assembly relaxing and satisfying. It's the perfect activity to unwind with after a long day or to enjoy as a peaceful weekend project. The sense of accomplishment upon completing the set is truly gratifying.The versatility of this set as a piece of home decor is fantastic. It looks great in any room, adding a touch of greenery without the need for watering or sunlight. The artificial plants are a clever solution for those who love the look of indoor plants but may not have the time or conditions to maintain real ones.It's also an excellent conversation starter. Guests are often surprised to learn that the succulents are made of LEGO pieces, which leads to interesting discussions about the set and its construction.The quality of the LEGO pieces is, as always, top-notch. The colors are vibrant, and the pieces fit together seamlessly, creating sturdy and durable plant models.In summary, the LEGO Icons Succulents 10309 Set is a wonderful purchase for anyone looking for a unique, creative, and stylish addition to their home. It's not just a building set; it's a piece of decor that brings a sense of joy and satisfaction. This set would also make a fantastic gift for a LEGO enthusiast or anyone who appreciates a bit of whimsy in their home. Highly recommended for its therapeutic building experience and its charming end result!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beauty that lasts and fun to build!
reviews.reviewText: We have several of the Lego “ornamentals” and this is tied with the orchid for most visually striking.I left the kit on a table over the holidays and invited anyone who wanted a few minutes of quiet to spend some time assembling one part of it. In the end, five different family members had a hand in building the finished item, which means it’s not just beautiful, it has special memories to go with it.Because there are nine individual plants, each one of them is straightforward and rewarding for whoever builds it.I highly recommend this both for the fun of making it and the fact that it creates something beautiful which even my horrible gardening skills can’t under/over-water!!

reviews.reviewText: I love this lego set! It’s a cute addition to my growing PC desk setup. It will add a nice flare to any corner you place it on. It took me like 2.5-3 hours to build, very easy! reviews.reviewTitle: Entretenido, Hermoso y Articulo de Decoracion
